vernac_cmds: Parameter Join_F: forall A, Join (F A).
Parameter Perm_F: forall A, Perm_alg (F A).
Parameter Sep_F: forall A, Sep_alg (F A).
Axiom squash_unsquash : forall k:knot, squash (unsquash k) = k.
Axiom unsquash_squash : forall (n:nat) (f:F predicate), unsquash (squash (n,f)) = (n, fmap F (approx n) (approx n) f).
Axiom knot_age1 : forall k:knot, age1 k = match unsquash k with | (O,_) => None | (S n,x) => Some (squash (n,x)) end.
Axiom knot_level : forall k:knot, level k = fst (unsquash k).
Axiom unsquash_inj : forall k1 k2, unsquash k1 = unsquash k2 -> k1 = k2.
Axiom unsquash_approx : forall k n Fp, unsquash k = (n, Fp) -> Fp = fmap F (approx n) (approx n) Fp.
Axiom approx_approx1 : forall m n, approx n = approx n oo approx (m+n).
Axiom approx_approx2 : forall m n, approx n = approx (m+n) oo approx n.
Declare Module KSAI: KNOT_FULL_SA_INPUT with Module KI := KI.
Declare Module K: KNOT_BASIC with Module KI := KI.
Declare Module KL: KNOT_BASIC_LEMMAS with Module K := K.
Instance Join_nat_F: Join (nat * F predicate) := Join_prod nat (Join_equiv nat) (F predicate) _.
Instance Perm_nat_F : Perm_alg (nat * F predicate) := @Perm_prod nat _ _ _ (Perm_equiv _) (Perm_F _).
Instance Sep_nat_F : Sep_alg (nat * F predicate) := @Sep_prod nat _ _ _ (Sep_equiv _) (Sep_F predicate).
Axiom join_unsquash : forall x1 x2 x3 : knot, join x1 x2 x3 = join (unsquash x1) (unsquash x2) (unsquash x3).
Axiom core_unsquash : forall x, core x = squash (core (unsquash x)).

Module KnotFullSa (KSAI': KNOT_FULL_SA_INPUT) (K': KNOT_BASIC with Module KI:=KSAI'.KI) (KL': KNOT_BASIC_LEMMAS with Module K:=K'): KNOT_FULL_SA with Module KI := KSAI'.KI with Module KSAI := KSAI' with Module K:=K' with Module KL := KL'.
Instance Join_nat_F: Join (nat * F predicate) := Join_prod nat (Join_equiv nat) (F predicate) _.
Instance Perm_nat_F : Perm_alg (nat * F predicate) := @Perm_prod nat _ _ _ (Perm_equiv _) (Perm_F _).
Instance Sep_nat_F: Sep_alg (nat * F predicate) := @Sep_prod nat _ _ _ (Sep_equiv _) (Sep_F predicate).
Instance Join_knot : Join knot := Join_preimage knot (nat * F predicate) Join_nat_F unsquash.
Lemma join_unsquash : forall x1 x2 x3, join x1 x2 x3 = join (unsquash x1) (unsquash x2) (unsquash x3).
Instance Perm_knot : Perm_alg knot := Perm_preimage _ _ _ _ unsquash squash squash_unsquash unsquash_squash_join_hom.
Instance Sep_knot: Sep_alg knot := Sep_preimage _ _ _ unsquash squash squash_unsquash unsquash_squash_join_hom.
Lemma core_unsquash : forall x, core x = squash (core (unsquash x)).
Lemma age_join1 : forall x y z x' : K'.knot, join x y z -> age x x' -> exists y' : K'.knot, exists z' : K'.knot, join x' y' z' /\ age y y' /\ age z z'.
Lemma age_join2 : forall x y z z' : K'.knot, join x y z -> age z z' -> exists x' : K'.knot, exists y' : K'.knot, join x' y' z' /\ age x x' /\ age y y'.
Lemma unage_join1 : forall x x' y' z', join x' y' z' -> age x x' -> exists y, exists z, join x y z /\ age y y' /\ age z z'.
unfold join, Join_knot, Join_preimage, age in *; simpl in *.
revert H0; rewrite knot_age1; destruct (unsquash x) as [n f] eqn:?H; intros.
destruct (unsquash z') as [n0 f0] eqn:?H; intros.
destruct (paf_preserves_unmap_right paf_F (approx n) (approx n) f f1 f0) as [q [w [? [? ?]]]].
replace y' with (squash (n, fmap F (approx (S n)) (approx (S n)) q)); auto.
replace (approx n oo approx (S n)) with (approx n); [replace (approx (S n) oo approx n) with (approx n) |]; auto.
replace (S n) with (1 + n)%nat by trivial.
replace (S n) with (1 + n)%nat by trivial.
replace z' with (squash (n,fmap F (approx (S n)) (approx (S n)) w)); auto.
replace (approx n oo approx (S n)) with (approx n); [replace (approx (S n) oo approx n) with (approx n) |]; auto.
replace (S n) with (1 + n)%nat by trivial.
replace (S n) with (1 + n)%nat by trivial.
Lemma unage_join2 : forall z x' y' z', join x' y' z' -> age z z' -> exists x, exists y, join x y z /\ age x x' /\ age y y'.
unfold join, Join_knot, Join_preimage, age in *; simpl in *.
destruct (unsquash z) as [n f] eqn:?H; destruct (unsquash z') as [n0 f0] eqn:?H; destruct (unsquash y') as [n1 f1] eqn:?H; destruct (unsquash x') as [n2 f2] eqn:?H; intros.
destruct (paf_preserves_unmap_left paf_F (approx n) (approx n) f2 f1 f) as [wx [wy [? [? ?]]]]; auto.
split; rewrite knot_age1; rewrite unsquash_squash; f_equal; hnf.
replace (approx n oo approx (S n)) with (approx n); [replace (approx (S n) oo approx n) with (approx n) |]; auto.
replace (S n) with (1 + n)%nat by trivial.
replace (S n) with (1 + n)%nat by trivial.
replace (approx n oo approx (S n)) with (approx n); [replace (approx (S n) oo approx n) with (approx n) |]; auto.
replace (S n) with (1 + n)%nat by trivial.
replace (S n) with (1 + n)%nat by trivial.
